# LangChain ecosystem

- Use `@langchain/core` for prompts, messages, and runnables
- Install provider packages only when needed (`@langchain/openai`, etc.)
- Enable LangSmith tracing via env vars (`LANGCHAIN_TRACING_V2`, `LANGCHAIN_API_KEY`, `LANGCHAIN_PROJECT`)
- Prefer structured output (Zod schemas) over parsing free-form text when the task allows
- For multi-step or branching logic, reach for LangGraph instead of ad-hoc state machines

When adding tools or API integrations, keep each tool focused on one action and document its inputs/outputs.
